President Moon of South Korea warmly welcomes President Trump and Mrs. Trump to Korea and expresses his condolences regarding the tragic news from Texas. He congratulates President Trump on his upcoming one-year anniversary of his election victory and commends him on his efforts in leading international collaboration to counter the North Korea nuclear issue. President Trump thanks President Moon for the warm welcome and expresses his appreciation for the beautiful ceremony. He looks forward to successful talks and mentions his upcoming visit to China.